{"tid":2260244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"五大聯賽最年輕球隊：AC米蘭第一","createTime":"2020-10-27T12:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T01:48:33.000Z","uid":34571,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ae43835517cea294e939a145a1207388e17561f3","tid":2260244,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"《CIES足球天文台》近日統計了今季各支球隊平均年齡排名，其中歐洲五大聯賽中，AC米蘭以24.5歲排名第一，摩納哥以24.7歲排名第2位。<br />\n<br />\n  在歐洲五大聯賽中平均<span class=\"x-large\">年齡最小</span>的球隊為<span class=\"x-large\">AC米蘭</span>，全隊平均年齡為<span class=\"x-large\">24.5歲</span>。排名2-4位的為三家法甲球隊，分別是摩納哥（24.7歲）、蘭斯（24.8歲）和聖伊天（24.8歲）。<br />\n<br />\n  此外還有四家法甲球隊進入了榜單前20名，包括佈雷斯特（25.2歲）、尼斯（25.3歲）、里昂（25.6歲）和里爾（25.8歲）。前20名中有7家法甲球隊、5家德甲球隊、3家意甲球隊、3家英超球隊和2家西甲球隊。<br />\n<br />\n  蒙彼利埃（29.2歲）是法甲平均年齡最大的球隊，在五大聯賽中排名第6，波爾多（28.1歲）和馬賽（27.7歲）也相對較大。"},{"pid":"cd42347164161a0379af04627f35866272c14cdc","tid":2260244,"uid":38189,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"收爺啦 日撚日係度A米A米"},{"pid":"f66b4bca5ba3fee67f7a77c2947712db93ea2a5b","tid":2260244,"uid":11254,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"廢老拉高哂"},{"pid":"d0c41744e06d56a77007b45babfb7812008ece55","tid":2260244,"uid":127454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f66b4bca5ba3fee67f7a77c2947712db93ea2a5b","tid":2260244,"uid":11254,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"廢老拉高哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"廢老身體年齡24歲"},{"pid":"42e04f96b94f9bae6d092a98be276b0d1786cbbd","tid":2260244,"uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"Milan: 24.5<br />\nSpezia: 26.3<br />\nFiorentina: 26.7<br />\nNapoli: 27.4<br />\nUdinese: 27.4<br />\nBologna: 27.4<br />\nSassuolo: 27.8<br />\nTorino: 27.9<br />\nAtalanta: 28<br />\nSampdoria: 28.2<br />\nJuventus: 28.4<br />\nRome: 28.4<br />\nInter: 28.7<br />\nLazio: 2